Show HN: Hand-tracked ar lens based on my chihuahua, made in Snapchat LensStudio
text: I previously worked there and have good familiarity with how to make a hand-tracked experience work well but also it’s easy for anyone to make this using the handheld object template in Lens Studio.   Let me know if you have questions and I’d be happy to give out pointers or tips & tricks.  You write JavaScript code (or no code if you use a template and don’t modify it) and there’s a scene graph and cameras much like Unity.
